Euro Area to Stay Whole, EU Economic Commissioner Olli Rehn Says

-- B y   K a t i   P o h j a n p a l o
-- 
2011-10-07T07:37:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/euro-area-to-stay-whole-eu-economic-commissioner-olli-rehn-says.html
The euro area will stay whole, as any
breakup would be an “unmitigated disaster,” European Union
Economic Commissioner Olli Rehn said in a speech in Helsinki
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
